---
import MainLayout from "../layouts/MainLayout.astro";
---

<MainLayout title="Privacy Policy">
  <div class="bg-white mt-8 px-4">
    <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-6 text-gray-900">Privacy Policy</h2>

    <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mt-6 mb-4 text-gray-800">
      Responsible Entity
    </h2>
    <p class="mb-4 text-justify">
      Protecting your personal data is of utmost importance to us. We process
      your data exclusively based on the applicable legal regulations (GDPR, TKG
      2003). In this privacy policy, we provide you with the key details
      regarding data processing on our website.
    </p>
    <p class="mb-4">
      The entity responsible for data processing on this website is:
    </p>
    <p class="mb-6">
      <span class="block font-medium">Maximilian Zirps</span>
      <span class="block mt-2">Maximilian Zirps e.U.</span>
      <span class="block">Seitenstettengasse 5/37 A-1010 Vienna</span>
      <span class="block">FN 634463i</span>
      <span class="block">hello@maxzirps.at</span>
    </p>

    <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mt-6 mb-4 text-gray-800">Hosting</h2>
    <p class="mb-4 text-justify">
      Our website is hosted by Vercel Inc., a US-based provider of cloud
      infrastructure services. The servers are typically located within the EU,
      but it is possible that data may be transferred to the USA.
    </p>
    <p class="mb-4 text-justify">
      Vercel processes access data for our website on our behalf (e.g., IP
      address, browser information, access time). For more information about
      Vercel's data processing, please refer to their <a
        href="https://vercel.com/legal/privacy-policy"
        class="text-blue-600 hover:underline"
        target="_blank"
        rel="noopener noreferrer">privacy policy</a
      >.
    </p>
    <p class="mb-6 text-justify">
      The use of Vercel is in the interest of providing a secure and efficient
      delivery of our online offerings. This constitutes a legitimate interest
      as defined by Article 6(1)(f) of the GDPR.
    </p>

    <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mt-6 mb-4 text-gray-800">
      No Use of Cookies or Tracking
    </h2>
    <p class="mb-6 text-justify">
      Our website does not use cookies, analytics tools, or similar tracking
      technologies that collect personal data.
    </p>

    <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mt-6 mb-4 text-gray-800">Your Rights</h2>
    <p class="mb-6 text-justify">
      You have the right to access the data we store about you at any time, as
      well as the right to correct, delete, restrict processing, and transfer
      your data. If you believe that the processing of your data violates data
      protection law or that your data protection rights have been infringed,
      you can file a complaint with the relevant supervisory authority. In
      Austria, this is the Data Protection Authority.
    </p>

    <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mt-6 mb-4 text-gray-800">Contact</h2>
    <p>
      If you have questions about the processing of your data, please contact:
    </p>
    <p class="mt-4">
      <span class="block font-medium">Maximilian Zirps</span>
      <span class="block">hello@maxzirps.at</span>
    </p>
  </div>
</MainLayout>
